---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---
<section class="border-t border-border/60 py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-content px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="reveal mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <span class="section-label">Comparison</span>
      <h2 class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-3xl">See the difference</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-muted-foreground">How cbash compresses your daily shell workflow.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid items-stretch gap-5 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="reveal card-surface overflow-hidden rounded-md">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-border px-5 py-3 font-mono text-sm font-semibold">
          <Icon name="lucide:x" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#ff7a7a]" /> Without cbash
        </div>
        <pre class="overflow-x-auto p-5 font-mono text-[13px] leading-[1.9]" style="background:hsl(var(--terminal-bg));color:hsl(var(--terminal-text))"><code><span class="t-faint"># Pull all repositories</span>
for repo in */; do
  cd "$repo" && git pull && cd ..
done

<span class="t-faint"># Auto-commit changes</span>
git add . && git commit -m "update" && git push

<span class="t-faint"># Check listening ports</span>
lsof -i -P -n | grep LISTEN</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal card-surface overflow-hidden rounded-md" style="border-color:rgba(0,255,136,0.35)">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-border px-5 py-3 font-mono text-sm font-semibold">
          <Icon name="lucide:check" class="ink h-4 w-4" /> With cbash
        </div>
        <pre class="overflow-x-auto p-5 font-mono text-[13px] leading-[1.9]" style="background:hsl(var(--terminal-bg));color:hsl(var(--terminal-text))"><code><span class="t-ok">cbash git pull-all</span>
<span class="t-faint"># ✓ Pulled 12 repos in 3.2s</span>

<span class="t-ok">cbash git auto-commit "update"</span>
<span class="t-faint"># ✓ Committed &amp; pushed</span>

<span class="t-ok">cbash system ports</span>
<span class="t-faint"># → Lists all listening ports</span></code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
